{"tid":1596581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] Forever 21倒閉真相","createTime":"2019-09-26T14:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:39:47.000Z","uid":284432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a50cd76820cc15cc95ce0da9f2b7a27c5fc5eaf","tid":1596581,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"作為一個銀行撚，我見到最近有啲紅媒講Forever 21係因為示威者既出現而導致關閉。<br />\n<br />\n我只可以講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對無啲咁既事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為Forever 21其實係早1至2個月前已經有找數既問題，既然無錢找數，又邊會有供應商供貨？所以香港分店關門只係時間問題。"},{"pid":"dcf4ea6fc31fa577c22fea82ee90bf375e473da3","tid":1596581,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"一早要執<br />\n之前銅鑼灣又唔通關雨革事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7521a136af7f174b86bfc34ec379a4f79000fdcd","tid":1596581,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"日本都一樣全線執笠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.jp/entry/forever21_jp_5d8ad611e4b01c02ca609818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffingtonpost.jp%2Fentry%2Fforever21_jp_5d8ad611e4b01c02ca609818&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=33554ba4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.huffingtonpost.jp/entry/forever21_jp_5d8ad611e4b01c02ca609818</a>"},{"pid":"4c7bfd39b519763322cabb1446faecce1aeb62ed","tid":1596581,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7521a136af7f174b86bfc34ec379a4f79000fdcd","tid":1596581,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"日本都一樣全線執笠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.jp/entry/forever21_jp_5d8ad611e4b01c02ca609818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffingtonpost.jp%2Fentry%2Fforever21_jp_5d8ad611e4b01c02ca609818&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D